you son of a bitch? You enjoy it?

02:12.541 --> 02:15.166
And there's Denver.
What are you gonna say to him?

02:15.250 --> 02:17.708
Tell him that he lost his son,
just like he lost his father?

02:17.791 --> 02:21.333
And both times
the same person was responsible, you!

02:23.625 --> 02:25.083
Did you actually love her?

02:25.166 --> 02:26.500
Well, look at her.

02:26.583 --> 02:30.125
