didn't know where to start.

05:10.208 --> 05:14.208
PALAWAN, PHILIPPINES

05:14.291 --> 05:17.291
TWO MONTHS AFTER THE FIRST HEIST

05:35.250 --> 05:37.750
After the heist
at the Royal Mint of Spain,

05:37.833 --> 05:40.875
