07:03.541 --> 07:05.958
how to get the gold out
of a state's national reserve.

07:06.041 --> 07:07.500
In this instance, Spain.

07:08.208 --> 07:11.750
So we invite you to come with us
as we dive into the fascinating journey

07:11.833 --> 07:14.041
