TV stations are already streaming it live.

07:20.375 --> 07:21.375
Breaking news.

07:21.458 --> 07:24.041
The robbers say they emptied
the gold vault of the Bank of Spain,

07:24.125 --> 07:26.958
and they're about to show us live
exactly how they did it.

07:27.041 --> 07:29.083
